#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_regression.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.datasets.make\\_regression"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:1 of
msgid "Generate a random regression problem."
msgstr "生成一个随机回归问题。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:3 of
msgid ""
"The input set can either be well conditioned (by default) or have a low "
"rank-fat tail singular profile. See :func:`make_low_rank_matrix` for more"
" details."
msgstr ""
"输入集可以是良好条件的（默认）或者具有低秩-肥尾奇异值分布。详情请参见 :"
"func:`make_low_rank_matrix`。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:7 of
msgid ""
"The output is generated by applying a (potentially biased) random linear "
"regression model with `n_informative` nonzero regressors to the "
"previously generated input and some gaussian centered noise with some "
"adjustable scale."
msgstr ""
"输出通过将具有 `n_informative` 个非零回归系数的（可能带偏置的）随机线性"
"回归模型应用于先前生成的输入，并加上一些可调尺度的高斯中心噪声生成。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:12 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <sample_generators>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <sample_generators>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_regression.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:14 of
msgid "The number of samples."
msgstr "样本数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:16 of
msgid "The number of features."
msgstr "特征数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:18 of
msgid ""
"The number of informative features, i.e., the number of features used to "
"build the linear model used to generate the output."
msgstr "信息特征的数量，即用于构建生成输出的线性模型的特征数量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:21 of
msgid ""
"The number of regression targets, i.e., the dimension of the y output "
"vector associated with a sample. By default, the output is a scalar."
msgstr "回归目标的数量，即与样本关联的 y 输出向量的维度。默认情况下，输出是标量。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:24 of
msgid "The bias term in the underlying linear model."
msgstr "底层线性模型中的偏置项。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:26 of
msgid ""
"if not None:     The approximate number of singular vectors required to "
"explain most     of the input data by linear combinations. Using this "
"kind of     singular spectrum in the input allows the generator to "
"reproduce     the correlations often observed in practice. if None:     "
"The input set is well conditioned, centered and gaussian with     unit "
"variance."
msgstr ""
"如果不为 None：用于通过线性组合解释大部分输入数据所需的奇异向量的近似数量"
"。在输入中使用这种奇异谱可以使得生成器重现实际中常见的相关性。如果为 None"
"：输入集是良好条件的、中心化的且具有单位方差的高斯分布。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:27 of
msgid "if not None:"
msgstr "如果不为 None："

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:28 of
msgid ""
"The approximate number of singular vectors required to explain most of "
"the input data by linear combinations. Using this kind of singular "
"spectrum in the input allows the generator to reproduce the correlations "
"often observed in practice."
msgstr ""
"通过线性组合解释大部分输入数据所需的奇异向量的近似数量。在输入中使用这种"
"奇异谱可以使生成器重现实践中经常观察到的相关性。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:32 of
msgid "if None:"
msgstr "如果为 None："

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:33 of
msgid ""
"The input set is well conditioned, centered and gaussian with unit "
"variance."
msgstr "输入集是良态的，中心化的，且具有单位方差的高斯分布。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:36 of
msgid ""
"The relative importance of the fat noisy tail of the singular values "
"profile if `effective_rank` is not None. When a float, it should be "
"between 0 and 1."
msgstr ""
"如果 `effective_rank` 不为 None，则为奇异值分布中肥尾噪声部分的相对重要性"
"。当为浮点数时，应在 0 和 1 之间。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:40 of
msgid "The standard deviation of the gaussian noise applied to the output."
msgstr "应用于输出的高斯噪声的标准差。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:42 of
msgid "Shuffle the samples and the features."
msgstr "打乱样本和特征的顺序。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:44 of
msgid "If True, the coefficients of the underlying linear model are returned."
msgstr "如果为 True，则返回底层线性模型的系数。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:46 of
msgid ""
"Determines random number generation for dataset creation. Pass an int for"
" reproducible output across multiple function calls. See :term:`Glossary "
"<random_state>`."
msgstr ""
"确定数据集创建时的随机数生成方式。传入一个整数以在多次函数调用中获得可"
"重现的输出。参见 :term:`术语表 <random_state>`。"

#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.datasets.make_regression.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:51 of
msgid ""
"* **X** (*tensor of shape (n_samples, n_features)*) -- The input samples."
" * **y** (*tensor of shape (n_samples,) or (n_samples, n_targets)*) -- "
"The output values. * **coef** (*tensor of shape (n_features,) or "
"(n_features, n_targets)*) -- The coefficient of the underlying linear "
"model. It is returned only if   coef is True."
msgstr ""
"* **X** (*tensor of shape (n_samples, n_features)*) -- 输入样本。\n"
"* **y** (*tensor of shape (n_samples,) or (n_samples, n_targets)*) -- "
"输出值。\n"
"* **coef** (*tensor of shape (n_features,) or (n_features, n_targets)*) "
"-- 底层线性模型的系数。仅在 coef 为 True 时返回。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:51 of
msgid "**X** (*tensor of shape (n_samples, n_features)*) -- The input samples."
msgstr "**X** (*tensor of shape (n_samples, n_features)*) -- 输入样本。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:52 of
msgid ""
"**y** (*tensor of shape (n_samples,) or (n_samples, n_targets)*) -- The "
"output values."
msgstr ""
"**y** (*tensor of shape (n_samples,) or (n_samples, n_targets)*) -- 输出"
"值。"

#: maxframe.learn.datasets.samples_generator.make_regression:53 of
msgid ""
"**coef** (*tensor of shape (n_features,) or (n_features, n_targets)*) -- "
"The coefficient of the underlying linear model. It is returned only if "
"coef is True."
msgstr ""
"**coef** (*tensor of shape (n_features,) or (n_features, n_targets)*) -- "
"底层线性模型的系数。仅在 coef 为 True 时返回。"

